trans-unit.source: Represents an I/O handle that is bound to the system thread pool and enables low-level components to receive notifications for asynchronous I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: Representa um identificador de E/S associado ao pool de threads do sistema e permite que componentes de baixo nível recebam notificações para operações de E/S assíncronas.

trans-unit.source: Returns an unmanaged pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um ponteiro não gerenciado para uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: An object from which to create the <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> pointer.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto com base no qual o ponteiro <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> será criado.

trans-unit.source: Returns an unmanaged pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure using the callback state and buffers associated with the specified <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um ponteiro não gerenciado para uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> usando o estado de retorno de chamada e os buffers associados ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Threading.PreAllocatedOverlapped" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure.
trans-unit.target: Um ponteiro não gerenciado para uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: The unmanaged pointer returned by this method can be passed to the operating system in overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: O ponteiro não gerenciado retornado por esse método pode ser passado para o sistema operacional em operações de e/s sobrepostas.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure is fixed in physical memory until the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> estrutura é fixa na memória física até o <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> método é chamado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="preAllocated" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="preAllocated" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="preAllocated" /> is currently in use for another I/O operation.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="preAllocated" /> está em uso no momento para outra operação de E/S.

trans-unit.source: This method was called after the <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> was disposed.
trans-unit.target: Esse método foi chamado após o <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> ter sido descartado.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: - ou -

trans-unit.source: This method was called after <paramref name="preAllocated" /> was disposed.
trans-unit.target: Esse método foi chamado após o <paramref name="preAllocated" /> ter sido descartado.

trans-unit.source: A delegate that represents the callback method to invoke when the asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: Um delegado que representa o método de retorno de chamada a ser invocado quando a operação de E/S assíncrona é concluída.

trans-unit.source: A user-provided object that distinguishes this <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instance from other <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto fornecido pelo usuário que distingue essa instância <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> de outras instâncias <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: An object or array of objects that represent the input or output buffer for the operation, or <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto ou uma matriz de objetos que representam o buffer de entrada ou de saída para a operação ou <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Each object represents a buffer, such an array of bytes.
trans-unit.target: Cada objeto representa um buffer, como uma matriz de bytes.

trans-unit.source: Returns an unmanaged pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure, specifying a delegate that is invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation is complete, a user-provided object that supplies context, and managed objects that serve as buffers.
trans-unit.target: Retornará um ponteiro não gerenciado para uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />, especificando um delegado invocado quando a operação de E/S assíncrona for concluída, um objeto fornecido pelo usuário que oferece contexto e objetos gerenciados que funcionam como buffers.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure.
trans-unit.target: Um ponteiro não gerenciado para uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="callback" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="callback" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: This method was called after the <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> object was disposed.
trans-unit.target: Esse método foi chamado após o objeto <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> ter sido descartado.

trans-unit.source: An object that holds the operating system handle.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que contém o identificador do sistema operacional.

trans-unit.source: The handle must have been opened for overlapped I/O in unmanaged code.
trans-unit.target: O identificador deve ter sido aberto para a E/S sobreposta no código não gerenciado.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> for the specified handle, which is bound to the system thread pool.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> para o identificador especificado, associado ao pool de threads do sistema.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> for <paramref name="handle" />, which is bound to the system thread pool.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> para <paramref name="handle" />, associado ao pool de threads do sistema.

trans-unit.source: This method should be called once per handle.
trans-unit.target: Esse método deve ser chamado uma vez por identificador.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle> object does not take ownership of `handle`; it remains the responsibility of the caller to call <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.Dispose%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle> objeto não se apropriar `handle`; ele permanece a responsabilidade do chamador ao chamar <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.Dispose%2A>.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="handle" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="handle" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="handle" /> has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="handle" /> foi descartado.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: - ou -

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="handle" /> does not refer to a valid I/O handle.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="handle" /> não se refere a um identificador de E/S válido.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: - ou -

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="handle" /> refers to a handle that has not been opened for overlapped I/O.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="handle" /> se refere a um identificador que não foi aberto para E/S sobreposta.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: - ou -

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="handle" /> refers to a handle that has already been bound.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="handle" /> se refere a um identificador que já foi associado.

trans-unit.source: Releases all unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos não gerenciados usados pela instância <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" />.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure structure to be freed.
trans-unit.target: Um ponteiro não gerenciado para a estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> a ser liberada.

trans-unit.source: Frees the memory associated with a <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure allocated by the <see cref="Overload:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Libera a memória associada a uma estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> alocada pelo método <see cref="Overload:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: You must call the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> method exactly once on every <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> unmanaged pointer allocated by using the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Você deve chamar o <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> método exatamente uma vez em cada <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> ponteiro não gerenciado alocado usando o <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: If you do not call the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> method, you will leak memory.
trans-unit.target: Se você não chama o <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> método, você irá causar vazamento de memória.

trans-unit.source: If you call the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> method method more than once on the same <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> unmanaged pointer, memory will be corrupted.
trans-unit.target: Se você chamar o <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.FreeNativeOverlapped%2A> mais de uma vez no mesmo método <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> ponteiro não gerenciado, memória seja corrompida.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="overlapped" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="overlapped" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: This method was called after the <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> object was disposed.
trans-unit.target: Esse método foi chamado após o objeto <see cref="T:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle" /> ter sido descartado.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> structure from which to return the associated user-provided object.
trans-unit.target: Um ponteiro não gerenciado para a estrutura <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> por meio da qual o objeto fornecido pelo usuário associado será retornado.

trans-unit.source: Returns the user-provided object that was specified when the <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instance was allocated by calling the <see cref="M:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped(System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback,System.Object,System.Object)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o objeto fornecido pelo usuário especificado quando a instância <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> foi alocada chamando o método <see cref="M:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped(System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback,System.Object,System.Object)" />.

trans-unit.source: A user-provided object that distinguishes this <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instance from other <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> instances, or <see langword="null" /> if one was not specified when the intstance was allocated by calling the <see cref="Overload:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto fornecido pelo usuário que distingue essa instância <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> de outras instâncias <see cref="T:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped" /> ou <see langword="null" /> se um objeto não foi especificado quando a instância foi alocada chamando o método <see cref="Overload:System.Threading.ThreadPoolBoundHandle.AllocateNativeOverlapped" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="overlapped" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="overlapped" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the bound operating system handle.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o identificador do sistema operacional associado.

trans-unit.source: An object that holds the bound operating system handle.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que retém o identificador do sistema operacional associado.
